---
// CondoCombat Hero — tagline satírica em duas colunas
---

<section class="w-full bg-slate-50 px-4 py-20 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 md:py-32">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl md:grid md:grid-cols-2 md:items-center md:gap-12">
    <!-- Left Column: Copy -->
    <div class="text-center md:text-left">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900 md:text-5xl">
        Seu condomínio é um circo?
        <span class="text-rose-600">Nós temos o palhaço.</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-500">
        O ERP que organiza fofocas, rastreia rixas e transforma o caos
        condominial em dados acionáveis.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col items-center gap-4 sm:flex-row md:justify-start">
        <a
          href="https://app.condocombat.com"
          class="rounded-xl bg-rose-600 px-6 py-3 text-base font-semibold text-white shadow-sm transition-colors hover:bg-rose-700"
        >
          Começar Agora
        </a>
        <a
          href="#recursos"
          class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white px-6 py-3 text-base font-semibold text-slate-700 shadow-sm transition-colors hover:border-rose-200"
        >
          Saiba Mais
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Right Column: Decorative illustration -->
    <div class="mt-12 hidden md:block">
      <div class="rounded-2xl bg-rose-50 p-8">
        <!-- Condo chaos dashboard mockup -->
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <!-- Card: Rivalidade Ativa -->
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 rounded-xl bg-white p-4 shadow-sm">
            <div class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-red-100 text-lg">
              🔥
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <p class="text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-400">
                Rivalidade Ativa
              </p>
              <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900">
                3º Andar vs 4º Andar
              </p>
            </div>
            <span class="rounded-full bg-red-50 px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-medium text-red-600">
              Crítica
            </span>
          </div>

          <!-- Card: Fofoca do Dia -->
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 rounded-xl bg-white p-4 shadow-sm">
            <div class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-amber-100 text-lg">
              🗣️
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <p class="text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-400">
                Fofoca do Dia
              </p>
              <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900">
                Vizinho do 201 mudou o gato de nome
              </p>
            </div>
            <span class="rounded-full bg-amber-50 px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-medium text-amber-600">
              Nova
            </span>
          </div>

          <!-- Card: Multas Pendentes -->
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 rounded-xl bg-white p-4 shadow-sm">
            <div class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-rose-100 text-lg">
              🚨
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <p class="text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-400">
                Multas Pendentes
              </p>
              <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900">
                12 notificações esta semana
              </p>
            </div>
            <span class="rounded-full bg-rose-50 px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-medium text-rose-600">
              Urgente
            </span>
          </div>

          <!-- Card: Próxima Assembleia -->
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 rounded-xl bg-white p-4 shadow-sm">
            <div class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-emerald-100 text-lg">
              📋
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <p class="text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-400">
                Próxima Assembleia
              </p>
              <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900">
                Sábado — Tema: Barulho após 22h
              </p>
            </div>
            <span class="rounded-full bg-emerald-50 px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-medium text-emerald-600">
              Confirmado
            </span>
          </div>

          <!-- Card: Status do Condomínio -->
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 rounded-xl bg-white p-4 shadow-sm">
            <div class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-violet-100 text-lg">
              👀
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <p class="text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-400">
                Caos Geral
              </p>
              <div class="mt-1 flex items-center gap-1">
                <div class="h-2 w-full rounded-full bg-slate-200">
                  <div class="h-2 w-4/5 rounded-full bg-rose-500"></div>
                </div>
                <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-rose-600">84%</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
